name: BadPunMonday
0:
”Alexa ask Bad Pun Monday for a pun”
”Alexa start Bad Pun Monday”
”Alexa ask Bad Pun Monday tell me a pun”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bad pun monday
des:
Some people like puns, some people don't. Whether you like them or not, these puns are pretty bad and should be reserved for Mondays. 

Now you can ask Alexa to have Bad Pun Monday tell you a pun any day of the week.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
